the seasons first named storm 
tropical storm arthur swirled to life tuesday in the caribbean 
east of trinidad 
the government of the nation of trinidad and tobago issued storm 
warnings for trinidad tobago grenada and grenada dependencies 
the islands separate the southeastern caribbean sea from the 
