radio stations in miami for inciting the incidents at the 
embassies the first incident occurred at the czechoslovak embassy 
on july 9 
cuban reports said at least three of the exile radio stations 
can often be heard clearly in havana but the cuban reports were 
unable to substantiate vieras claims that they have been been 
encouraging cubans to seek refuge 
the reporters said one of the stations is operated by the 
