hopkinton nh a member of the congregation kathy pepin said he 
always helps a woman in a wheelchair 
every single sunday he wheels her out of the church and brings 
her to her car always joking and laughing with her at the same 
time she said 
friends say souter has a parsimonious nature despite a net 
worth of over 600000 he drove cars until they were rusty with 
age 
when he goes mountain climbing with his law clerks said lawyer 
jack middleton they come back dragging their tongues 
