has described himself as an investigative freelance reporter 
helped spread the rumors 
casey 45 was arrested monday on a south dakota warrant for 
allegedly writing an insufficientfund check 23 months ago the 
arrest came less than an hour after he finished testifying before 
the federal grand jury in omaha 
