the federal racketeering and gambling trial 
of new orleans district attorney a former federal attorney a 
television actor and others went to a jury tuesday 
jurors will begin deliberations wednesday 
at the heart of the sixweek trial was the allegation that 
district attorney harry connick illegally returned seized gambling 
records to known bookmaker walton aucoin so aucoin could pay off 
and collect gambling debts 
on trial with connick are actor paul burke and former assistant 
us attorney patrick fanning aucoin also is a codefendant along 
