a sharp turnaround on stock market psychology is 
seen as a key reason for the latest jolt by the dow jones 
industrial average the nations bestknown stock barometer had 
toyed with breaking a record high just a week ago 
the average plunged more than 100 points within the first 90 
minutes of trading on monday recouped part of the loss and yoyoed 
through much of the day in heavy trading it finished down 5654 
points to 290470 
