californias aerospace industry 
northrop officials said mondays speech by rep les aspin 
dwis is just the latest word in a long debate over the bombers 
importance as the cold war ends 
defense secretary dick cheney has proposed building 75 b2s 
down from the 132 originally envisioned 
so far only one b2 has been completed and it would take 
several years for the program to be phased out even if aspin and 
other opponents cap production at 15 operational planes 
