<TEXT>
continental airlines announced it is cutting its 
nationwide fares up to 57 percent during the next three weekends 
the houstonbased carriers sale fares range from 39 to 129 
one way they are first available for travel beginning thursday 
friday or saturday and ending saturday sunday or monday 
continental said the fares also apply to travel beginning aug 
24 and returning aug 46 and beginning aug 911 and returning 
aug 1113 
the sale fares are available on virtually all mainland us 
flights and some international flights 
for example the fare from boston to austin texas will be 99 
each way compared with a regular low fare of 182 each way thats 
a savings of 46 percent 
continental also is offering some international weekend sale 
fares the sale fare from houston to acapulco is 69 each way 
while travel from newark nj to bermuda is 99 each way 
the enormous popularity of our most recent weekend sale fares 
for travel between hub cities have encouraged us to offer a weekend 
sale for travel nationwide a continental spokesman said 
continental said seats are limited tickets must be purchased on 
tuesday or wednesday and within 24 hours of making a reservation 
a roundtrip purchase is required and tickets are 
nonrefundable travel must occur on the same weekend 
